messages.message: Do you know I saw you last semester and just wasn't sure if it was you or not.  By the way my friend Laura says your kind of cute.

Brian
I didn't even know you went here!  Are you a sophmore?  I think you're older then me.  Wow, it's so great to see a familiar face, we should hang out sometime!
Lol, yes I am older than you silly, I turn 25 this year, I am so old.  And I am a junior.  But I didn't come up here until this year.

Brian
Ohh, cool.  How do you like it so far?  I think it sucks because it's freezing cold everyday but it refuses to snow.  What are you majoring in?  Still working at Slaveway?
I love it, but then I don't think its cold.  I am majoring in Archaeology, what about you?  Yes I still work at Safeway, I am actually working at the one up here.
